annotationA: 60S ribosomal protein L9; Structural constituent of ribosome; rRNA binding. It is involved in the biological process described with: mitotic spindle elongation; translation; centrosome duplication; mitotic spindle organization; Belongs to the universal ribosomal protein uL6 family
annotationB: 40S ribosomal protein S18; Located at the top of the head of the 40S subunit, it contacts several helices of the 18S rRNA
